Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}眠り解きあぐねて　君を見失い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}漫长沉睡中醒来 却发现失去了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}壊したくなる今すべて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}此刻恨不能破坏一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:20.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}望む言葉が二度と聞けないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:20.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若再也听不到 那令人心动的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:26.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}命さえ無為に差し出すでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:26.80,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我宁愿徒然付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:34.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}消えそうな輝きへと寄り添う想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:34.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心绪飘向那若隐若现的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:41.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}孤独だよ　私の元にも朝日がくるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:41.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一阵孤独 是否我亦能拥有明日朝阳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:48.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}答えて…ふたりを繋ぐ愛があると
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:48.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}告诉我 我们之间还有爱相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:55.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}招かれた絶望の果てに立ち向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:55.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}让我能直面眼前那无尽绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:02:02.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}産まれて滅びる人の意識こそが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:02:02.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}正是生而即逝的人之意识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:12.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}未来を選び　鍵を開ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:12.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}才能选择未来 打开那心锁

Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:22:03.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}満ちる哀しみすべて 風に預けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:22:03.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}将满溢的哀愁都寄托于风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:10.22,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}奏でよう 優しいSerenade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.86,0:22:10.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}请奏响那温柔的小夜曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:16.29,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}きっと　願うこの心が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:16.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}这颗祈愿的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:27.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}何より確かな永遠の道標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:27.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一定是最精确的永恒路标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:31.00,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}増えてゆく罪の海に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.53,0:22:31.00,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}罪之海潮起潮落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:37.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光の嵐よ舞いあがれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:37.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}等待一场光辉的风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:41.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに傷だらけでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:41.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}即便已然伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:44.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}走り続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:44.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我依然继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:48.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}嘆きの雨を 孤独の朝を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:48.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}无论叹息之雨 还是孤独清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:53.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}駆け抜け僕らは出会える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:53.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我们终将穿越它而邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:23:00.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}流れる星の声が 希望降らせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:23:00.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}流淌的星辰之声 将降下希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:03.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}飛ぶ立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:03.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:09.06,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}始まるよTruth Of My Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:09.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}即将开始的Truth Of My Destiny
